Note this app is very rough and ready. It will need to be tidied before it can be used to demo externally.

## Running the Python app locally
### Install dependencies in virtualenv
```
cd payments_api_demo
virtualenv -p python3 venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
```

### Run the app
'''
python app/app.py
'''

## Build docker image and deploy to AWS
'''
make build
make tag
make push
make deploy
'''

You can view the deployed app at: http://payments-api-demo.us-west-2.elasticbeanstalk.com/

